channel.title: Looking for a partner to
channel.description:
Hi, I am back to this forums now. After my computer was broken when I got it fixed he just asked me to help him make a private server for World of Warcraft server. This has not been put public yet due to us still doing a few more tweeks to it. That was interesting so, I have finaly come back to this forums and now I am here to create a runescape private server.
Things I want on this server will be the following.
~The least amount of public voids possible ~Dedicated server. I will be paying for this once I think we are ready. (Friend said I can go halfers on the 2 servers he is paying for when he brings his WoW server public.) ~Good economy ~Good PVPing ~Perfect specials ~No "Silabs items" ~Eventually a client
If you want to join me you must go and download Vent. I will PM you the information to the server I will be using.
Thank you, for taking the time to read this.
~Spidaz
edit~ Please no flam,spam, or cursing in this thread Thank you
